high_descs: Take left, walk to table
Take the knife with yellow handle off the table
Turn around, walk to fridge, take left, walk to counter
Slice the apple on the counter with knife
Take left, walk to end of counter, take a right
Stab the knife near the scrubby on the counter
Take right, walk back to apple, turn to counter
Take one of the three slices of apple
Turn around in a circle, walk to stove top
Place apple slice in pan on right
Grab pan with apple slice
walk back over to knife stabbing scrubby on counter
Place pan behind knife on counter
anns.task_desc: Slice apple to place part of it in a pan

high_descs: turn to the left
pick up the knife from the brown table
turn around to the right
face the counter slice an apple that is on the counter
turn to the left
leave the knife on the counter
turn to the right
pick up a slice of the apple
turn to the left and across the room face the stove
put the piece of apple inside the pot that is on the stove
pick up the pot from the stove
turn to the left and across the room
put the  pot on the counter
anns.task_desc: slice an apple putting it in on a stove on the counter

high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the right side of the wood table.
Take the large knife to the right of the fork.
Turn around, go forward, turn left and go forward to the counter between the sink and the oven.
Cut the apple on the counter into pieces.
Turn left, go forward, turn right between the sink and the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the knife on the counter near the sponge.
Turn right, go back to the counter with the cut apple.
Take a piece of apple from the counter.
Turn right, go forward, turn left to face the right side of the oven.
Put the apple in the pot on the right of the stove top.
Take the pot from the stove top.
Turn left, go forward, turn right between the sink and the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the pot to the right of the microwave, close to the back wall.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a piece of apple in it on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left and face the table with the silverware on it.
Pick up the knife that is to the right of the fork.
Turn around and walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Use the knife to cut the apple on the counter into thirds.
Turn left and carry the knife to the counter on the other side of the sink.
Place the knife on top of the sponge.
Turn right and walk back to the counter with the sliced apple on top of it.
Pick up one of the apple pieces.
Take the apple piece to the stove.
Put the apple piece in the pot on the lower right burner of the stove.
Pick up the pot with the apple piece inside.
Carry the pot with the apple piece inside to the counter with the knife and sponge on it.
Place the pot with the apple piece inside on the counter behind the sponge and knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a piece of apple inside of it on a counter behind a sponge.

high_descs: Walk forward, turn ninety degrees, then walk to the brown table on the left
Pick up the knife off of the table
Turn around, walk forward, turn left, walk to the counter
Use the knife to slice the apple
Turn left, walk forward, turn right in front of the sponge
Place the knife on the table
Turn right, walk forward, turn left to the counter in front of the apple
Take a piece of the apple
Turn around, walk left, turn left in front of the stove
Place the apple in the pot
Pick up the pot with the apple in it
Turn left, walk forward, turn right to the counter
Place pot on table behind the sponge and knife
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple, put it into a pot, place the pot by the microwave

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the wooden table.
Pick the knife with a golden handle up off the table.
Turn around, walk forward then take a left and walk over to the counter with an apple on it.
Slice the apple on the counter.
Turn left and walk over to where the sponge is on the counter.
Put the knife tip down into the counter next to the sponge.
Turn to the right and walk back over to the apple.
Pick up a sliced piece of apple.
Turn to the right and walk over to the pot on the stove.
Place the sliced piece of apple  into the pot.
Pick the pot with the sliced apple in it up off the stove.
Turn to the left and walk over to the part of the counter where the sponge and knife are.
Place the pot to the left on the counter behind the sponge and knife.
anns.task_desc: Place the pot with a piece of sliced apple in it on the counter.
